WEBVTT

00:00:00.540 --> 00:00:02.120
Hayase-san has nothing to do with this.

00:00:02.120 --> 00:00:05.460
You have until tonight.

00:00:05.460 --> 00:00:08.840
Ichika's the one who suggested we reboot you.

00:00:08.840 --> 00:00:10.680
- Mayu-san!
- I only put her to sleep.

00:00:10.680 --> 00:00:15.230
If you want to save her,
bring Riku Hayase to the location I specify.

00:00:15.230 --> 00:00:16.250
You have until 10 p.m.

00:00:16.250 --> 00:00:18.300
- Do you have a gun?
- There's one at your place.

00:00:18.300 --> 00:00:23.090
I'll have you know, we have a search warrant.

00:00:23.090 --> 00:00:26.620
We'll hear more from you at the office.

00:00:26.620 --> 00:00:33.470
Timing and subtitles by
"🍰 The Pastry Detectives 🔍" Team @Viki.com

00:00:33.470 --> 00:00:35.150
We're running out of time.

00:00:35.150 --> 00:00:37.910
Gido can't save Mayu-san alone.

00:00:37.910 --> 00:00:40.480
Do I tell the police everything?

00:00:40.480 --> 00:00:41.960
Do I tell them Gido was alive

00:00:41.960 --> 00:00:45.790
and pray his testimony proves my innocence?

00:00:45.790 --> 00:00:50.090
No, I can't. Goroku wouldn't let that slide.

00:00:50.090 --> 00:00:54.060
First things first, we have to save Mayu-san.

00:00:57.410 --> 00:00:59.220
Sit.

00:01:04.690 --> 00:01:09.020
You are to remain here
while we search your confiscated items.

00:01:10.880 --> 00:01:14.610
Goroku's people have a citizen held hostage.

00:01:17.500 --> 00:01:19.560
This is where she's being kept.

00:01:19.560 --> 00:01:22.000
Please, go save her.

00:01:24.610 --> 00:01:27.820
The hostage is a woman named Mayu Gido.

00:01:27.820 --> 00:01:29.940
She is my wife.

00:01:32.400 --> 00:01:35.090
Team A, reaching the top of the stairs.

00:01:35.090 --> 00:01:37.690
Team B, right behind you.

00:01:37.690 --> 00:01:38.830
Police!

00:01:38.830 --> 00:01:40.820
Freeze!

00:01:56.450 --> 00:01:58.220
Did you find her?

00:02:02.280 --> 00:02:05.980
Why send us on a wild-goose chase, Gido?

00:02:07.010 --> 00:02:08.640
What?

00:02:09.510 --> 00:02:14.430
The location you specified was deserted.

00:02:18.510 --> 00:02:23.470
I suppose you're finally getting desperate.

00:02:27.460 --> 00:02:32.160
Right. Goroku's spy.

00:02:43.400 --> 00:02:45.040
Hello?

00:02:45.040 --> 00:02:47.790
We passed on the new location to Gido.

00:02:47.790 --> 00:02:50.490
Now we wait.

00:02:50.490 --> 00:02:52.260
All right, sounds good.

00:02:53.660 --> 00:02:56.930
Should we open that Burgundy we received?
[Hinako Goroku]

00:02:56.930 --> 00:02:59.110
Great idea.

00:03:01.100 --> 00:03:04.300
Pizza's served, kids.

00:03:04.300 --> 00:03:07.490
- Yes!
- Wow!

00:03:07.490 --> 00:03:09.810
- Daddy, give me a slice!
- There you go.

00:03:09.810 --> 00:03:11.140
- Thanks!
- You get the big slice, Dear.

00:03:11.140 --> 00:03:13.840
- Thank you.
- No, thank you.

00:03:13.840 --> 00:03:15.300
Anytime.

00:03:15.300 --> 00:03:17.480
- Daddy, hurry!
- Yes, Sweetie.

00:03:17.480 --> 00:03:21.210
- Hot.
- Yum!

00:03:24.320 --> 00:03:26.160
- Give me a minute.
- Sure.

00:03:26.160 --> 00:03:27.530
Hello?

00:03:27.530 --> 00:03:30.260
I knocked out your men out front.

00:03:31.070 --> 00:03:34.860
If you don't let me in,
your family will pay the price.

00:03:44.280 --> 00:03:47.030
- A guest?
- That would be for me.

00:03:50.450 --> 00:03:52.210
Come on in.

00:03:52.210 --> 00:03:54.580
[Unlocked]

00:03:56.980 --> 00:03:59.290
I have an unexpected guest.

00:04:09.090 --> 00:04:11.770
Long time no see, Gido-san.

00:04:13.320 --> 00:04:15.610
Good evening.

00:04:17.960 --> 00:04:22.550
It's a pleasure to meet you.
I am Goroku's wife.

00:04:22.550 --> 00:04:24.680
Evening, Ma'am. I apologize for intruding.

00:04:24.680 --> 00:04:26.860
- Please, come on in.
- Yes, welcome in.

00:04:26.860 --> 00:04:28.810
- I'll see him in my room.
- Sure.

00:04:28.810 --> 00:04:30.710
I'll bring you both drinks.

00:04:30.710 --> 00:04:33.130
Thank you, but I won't be staying long.

00:04:35.820 --> 00:04:37.610
Follow me.

00:04:40.510 --> 00:04:42.130
Come on in.

00:04:53.680 --> 00:04:57.400
The real deal sure is intimidating.

00:04:57.400 --> 00:04:59.960
I'll cut straight to the chase.

00:04:59.960 --> 00:05:03.360
Ichika kidnapped my wife.

00:05:04.440 --> 00:05:06.970
She couldn't have managed such a feat alone.

00:05:06.970 --> 00:05:10.110
You must have made Fuyuhashi help.

00:05:10.110 --> 00:05:13.090
Getting a citizen involved is risky,

00:05:13.090 --> 00:05:17.160
but it was a necessary risk to take.

00:05:17.160 --> 00:05:19.020
Come on in.

00:05:26.060 --> 00:05:27.430
Thank you, Dear.

00:05:27.430 --> 00:05:33.060
My husband made pizza tonight.
Care for a slice?

00:05:33.060 --> 00:05:34.110
Looks delicious.

00:05:34.110 --> 00:05:37.190
It's one of our children's favorites.

00:05:38.240 --> 00:05:42.110
- Thank you.
- We appreciate your visit tonight.

00:05:42.930 --> 00:05:45.660
- Sorry.
- It's fine.

00:05:45.660 --> 00:05:48.940
- Did you drive here?
- No.

00:05:48.940 --> 00:05:51.250
Then drink up.

00:05:58.480 --> 00:06:00.030
Enjoy your stay.

00:06:00.030 --> 00:06:02.300
Thank you.

00:06:11.840 --> 00:06:14.200
Eat up while it's hot.

00:06:19.030 --> 00:06:22.240
I won't kill you while my family's around.

00:06:24.520 --> 00:06:26.790
Let's hear your story.

00:06:34.820 --> 00:06:40.580
I'm not the one who stole the billion
three years ago.

00:06:40.580 --> 00:06:44.320
Didn't you reboot Riku Hayase
as a part of your grand escape?

00:06:44.320 --> 00:06:48.380
Ichika's the one who suggested we reboot him.

00:06:48.380 --> 00:06:53.160
You used Hayase to steal ten billion from us.

00:06:53.160 --> 00:06:56.320
The riches I stole were all junk.

00:06:58.530 --> 00:07:01.440
Ichika had them swapped them out.

00:07:01.440 --> 00:07:04.080
She's leading you down a false trail.

00:07:04.080 --> 00:07:06.390
Are you saying Ichika is our culprit?

00:07:08.890 --> 00:07:11.800
I understand you won't believe me,

00:07:11.800 --> 00:07:15.830
but torturing me won't bring the money back.

00:07:15.830 --> 00:07:18.520
That ten billion will remain missing.

00:07:20.110 --> 00:07:23.580
Mr. Ma of the Hong Kong gang
entrusted you with those riches.

00:07:23.580 --> 00:07:27.090
Lose his trust, and he'll hunt you down.

00:07:27.090 --> 00:07:30.140
Mr. Ma will be plenty satisfied
with the neck of our culprit.

00:07:30.140 --> 00:07:35.280
I'll repay the ten billion over time.

00:07:39.020 --> 00:07:42.310
Give me a chance to speak with Ichika, alone.

00:07:42.310 --> 00:07:46.500
I can get her to fess up about the riches.

00:07:46.500 --> 00:07:48.350
Just please, release Mayu.

00:07:48.350 --> 00:07:51.520
Gido-san, you've reached your limits.

00:07:51.520 --> 00:07:55.250
Cough up the money while you still can.

00:07:58.010 --> 00:08:00.860
Fine. I'll take it a step further.

00:08:02.300 --> 00:08:05.930
I'll take you hostage
and prove myself innocent.

00:08:14.080 --> 00:08:15.840
Bastard...

00:08:19.200 --> 00:08:21.260
Goroku!

00:08:26.140 --> 00:08:31.340
My wife knows nothing of my line of work,

00:08:31.340 --> 00:08:35.910
but she's a lady who catches on quick.

00:08:35.910 --> 00:08:39.670
I've taught her what to do
when I have "visitors."

00:08:41.620 --> 00:08:44.290
Goroku...

00:08:47.010 --> 00:08:50.880
I don't get to have dinner with family often.

00:08:50.880 --> 00:08:54.210
But the pizza has gone ice-cold by now.

00:08:56.900 --> 00:09:02.050
- Kids, I have an idea.
- Yes?

00:09:02.050 --> 00:09:04.660
Since school is off tomorrow,

00:09:04.660 --> 00:09:06.850
how about we book a hotel,

00:09:06.850 --> 00:09:12.840
and spend the day at a waterpark?

00:09:12.840 --> 00:09:14.530
Is that fine by you, Dear?

00:09:16.880 --> 00:09:21.920
Yes! Yes!

00:09:21.920 --> 00:09:26.280
Okay, but let's clear up the table first.

00:09:26.280 --> 00:09:27.750
- Okay!
- Right, good idea.

00:09:27.750 --> 00:09:30.060
No jumping on the couch.

00:09:36.780 --> 00:09:38.480
Was everything okay?

00:09:38.480 --> 00:09:40.600
Yes.

00:09:40.600 --> 00:09:44.030
Please keep your business out of the house.

00:09:44.030 --> 00:09:45.660
Sorry.

00:10:13.400 --> 00:10:17.600
Gido was caught at Goroku's place.

00:10:17.600 --> 00:10:20.610
He'll be brought here shortly.

00:10:25.900 --> 00:10:29.000
You look worried.

00:10:30.410 --> 00:10:34.400
Don't want to see your lover get killed?

00:10:34.400 --> 00:10:36.400
No.

00:10:36.400 --> 00:10:40.800
I'm just surprised
he's so protective of his wife.

00:10:47.720 --> 00:10:52.900
[Ayumi Gido, Reboot, Day 6]

00:10:52.900 --> 00:10:55.000
Is Mayu-san all right?

00:10:55.000 --> 00:10:57.500
Did Gido manage to save her?

00:10:57.500 --> 00:11:01.400
No, focus on dealing with this first.

00:11:01.400 --> 00:11:04.900
The police definitely found Gido's gun.

00:11:04.900 --> 00:11:07.700
How do I talk my way out of this?

00:11:09.850 --> 00:11:11.150
Chief Mikami.

00:11:11.150 --> 00:11:14.980
I was called here as your direct superior.

00:11:14.980 --> 00:11:19.190
It's been a while
since I've worked until this hour.

00:11:21.230 --> 00:11:23.160
Bet you never thought

00:11:23.160 --> 00:11:27.820
your own subordinate
would send the hounds after you, right?

00:11:33.720 --> 00:11:37.010
In any case, you're free to go.

00:11:37.010 --> 00:11:40.900
Nothing suspicious was found in your room.

00:11:42.720 --> 00:11:47.310
I apologize for causing you trouble, Sir.

00:11:47.310 --> 00:11:51.960
We'll chalk it up to a rookie mistake.

00:11:51.960 --> 00:11:56.100
All right, anyone down for a round of drinks?

00:11:56.100 --> 00:11:57.200
I'd rather not, Sir.

00:11:57.200 --> 00:11:58.400
My bed calls for me.

00:11:58.400 --> 00:12:01.180
Likewise.

00:12:03.310 --> 00:12:07.520
It seems we were off our mark. What a shame.

00:12:07.520 --> 00:12:08.990
Something isn't adding up.

00:12:08.990 --> 00:12:13.100
He was clearly panicking
when we were searching his place.

00:12:13.100 --> 00:12:18.700
Perhaps Gido isn't the only one here

00:12:18.700 --> 00:12:22.480
with connections to Goroku's organization.

00:12:29.600 --> 00:12:31.400
Inspector Gido,

00:12:31.400 --> 00:12:33.500
I appreciated your cooperation tonight.

00:12:33.500 --> 00:12:35.600
Sir, I'm sorry, but I'm in a hurry.

00:12:35.600 --> 00:12:37.720
Hold on.

00:12:38.500 --> 00:12:40.400
You forgot something.

00:13:00.800 --> 00:13:04.800
I do not know "what" is within that bag

00:13:04.800 --> 00:13:08.000
nor do I want you to tell me what's in there.

00:13:08.000 --> 00:13:13.300
You took this from my place and hid it.

00:13:15.200 --> 00:13:18.700
You're Goroku's spy.

00:13:21.060 --> 00:13:23.350
Of course not.

00:13:23.350 --> 00:13:25.880
Then what does that make you, Sir?

00:13:57.800 --> 00:14:02.100
Your phone is tapped.

00:14:02.100 --> 00:14:03.790
What?

00:14:03.790 --> 00:14:07.260
It's most likely welded onto the battery.

00:14:07.260 --> 00:14:11.380
But wrap it in aluminum foil, like this...

00:14:12.780 --> 00:14:14.780
And we get our privacy.

00:14:14.780 --> 00:14:17.800
Here's your new phone.

00:14:17.800 --> 00:14:21.200
She's been monitoring me all this time.

00:14:21.200 --> 00:14:23.760
But don't go tossing away that device.

00:14:23.760 --> 00:14:27.540
Keep up the oblivious act, all right?

00:14:30.380 --> 00:14:36.000
I'll keep it brief.

00:14:36.000 --> 00:14:41.020
I can't have you disappearing on me.

00:14:42.240 --> 00:14:44.580
Six years ago,

00:14:44.580 --> 00:14:47.300
I discovered Inspector Gido

00:14:47.300 --> 00:14:53.000
was selling our intel to Fuyuhashi.

00:14:53.000 --> 00:14:55.420
But...

00:14:55.420 --> 00:14:58.300
instead of arresting Gido,
I chose to strike a deal with him.

00:14:59.440 --> 00:15:01.620
Inspector Gido.

00:15:01.620 --> 00:15:03.830
I'm not working

00:15:03.830 --> 00:15:08.300
to arrest some corrupt cop.

00:15:08.300 --> 00:15:12.100
I hope to reel in a bigger catch.

00:15:12.100 --> 00:15:15.740
Something like a whale, if you will.

00:15:15.740 --> 00:15:17.000
A whale?

00:15:17.000 --> 00:15:18.500
That's right.

00:15:18.500 --> 00:15:22.580
I'm referring to a certain politician
in line to become prime minister.

00:15:23.600 --> 00:15:27.600
Fuyuhashi works for Wataru Goroku.

00:15:27.600 --> 00:15:32.830
And we believe Goroku sends his dirty money
to said politician.

00:15:33.640 --> 00:15:39.180
But we don't have the evidence needed
to reel in the whale.

00:15:39.180 --> 00:15:43.810
If you can find me that evidence,
I will overlook your crimes.

00:15:44.620 --> 00:15:48.870
Make a deal like that,
and you'll be equally as guilty, sir.

00:15:49.800 --> 00:15:52.800
I believe it's worth the risk.

00:15:54.210 --> 00:15:56.490
So how about it?

00:15:56.490 --> 00:15:59.100
Will you be arrested where you stand?

00:15:59.100 --> 00:16:03.600
Or will you cooperate with me?

00:16:05.790 --> 00:16:10.530
Inspector Gido accepted my deal.

00:16:10.530 --> 00:16:15.860
He never brought me intel I could use.

00:16:15.860 --> 00:16:19.500
But his connections are crucial
for investigating the organization.

00:16:20.950 --> 00:16:23.160
You're a piece I cannot afford to lose.

00:16:23.160 --> 00:16:25.200
Inspector General Makita.

00:16:25.200 --> 00:16:27.550
What's all this about?

00:16:27.550 --> 00:16:29.730
Did you suddenly get nostalgic?

00:16:29.730 --> 00:16:32.000
I remember our deal loud and clear.

00:16:32.000 --> 00:16:34.600
Inspector Gido.

00:16:34.600 --> 00:16:40.200
Something felt off about you
when you first returned.

00:16:40.200 --> 00:16:42.700
So I sent your fingerprint out to forensics.

00:16:46.400 --> 00:16:48.800
I was quite shocked, Inspector.

00:16:49.980 --> 00:16:54.140
Your prints were those
of a certain man-on-the-run.

00:16:56.280 --> 00:16:58.200
You knew.

00:16:58.200 --> 00:17:00.310
- Good morning.
- I had hoped

00:17:00.310 --> 00:17:04.910
to carefully observe what you knew of me

00:17:04.910 --> 00:17:07.650
and figure out your motive for becoming Gido.

00:17:07.650 --> 00:17:11.360
Except our Second Investigation Team
decided to take action.

00:17:11.360 --> 00:17:15.170
Hearing word of their plan
to search your place,

00:17:15.170 --> 00:17:19.960
I circumvented them
and took "this" before they could.

00:17:20.780 --> 00:17:24.270
If you're asking how I let myself in,

00:17:25.090 --> 00:17:28.600
I had a spare key made of his place.

00:17:28.600 --> 00:17:32.700
I never quite trusted Gido, you see.

00:17:32.700 --> 00:17:36.450
I put on a front of doubt

00:17:36.450 --> 00:17:39.600
to protect him within the force.

00:17:39.600 --> 00:17:43.640
But I'm running out of ways to cover for him.

00:17:43.640 --> 00:17:47.730
We have to reel in that whale,
or we're both done for.

00:17:51.380 --> 00:17:54.620
Then you aren't Goroku's spy?

00:17:56.600 --> 00:17:59.800
No.

00:17:59.800 --> 00:18:06.200
I am a man of justice,
fighting against Goroku and his whale.

00:18:06.200 --> 00:18:11.700
One more piece of advice.
Be careful who you speak up to.

00:18:11.700 --> 00:18:14.800
Anyone could be the spy in here.

00:18:17.890 --> 00:18:20.870
I am innocent.

00:18:20.870 --> 00:18:23.900
I did not murder my wife.

00:18:25.200 --> 00:18:28.500
I have become like this because I was tricked.

00:18:28.500 --> 00:18:31.110
Gido-san will testify for me.

00:18:33.600 --> 00:18:35.690
Gido...

00:18:36.400 --> 00:18:38.100
is alive?

00:18:38.100 --> 00:18:40.300
He is.

00:18:40.300 --> 00:18:43.900
But he is being falsely accused
of stealing the organization's money.

00:18:43.900 --> 00:18:47.900
He and his wife are both about to be killed.

00:18:49.100 --> 00:18:51.400
Please, save them.

00:19:00.800 --> 00:19:03.500
I can't help you any more than I already have.

00:19:03.500 --> 00:19:06.600
- Why?
- Helping you here

00:19:06.600 --> 00:19:09.200
won't get me any closer to Goroku.

00:19:09.200 --> 00:19:13.100
Even if this eventually leads to his arrest,

00:19:13.100 --> 00:19:17.360
the whale backing him
will get him right out of jail.

00:19:17.360 --> 00:19:19.600
We only win when the whale is no more.

00:19:19.600 --> 00:19:21.400
And you call yourself a cop?

00:19:21.400 --> 00:19:23.600
People are going to die!

00:19:26.110 --> 00:19:29.820
Small sacrifices are necessary

00:19:29.820 --> 00:19:33.510
to save a great number of lives.

00:19:33.510 --> 00:19:36.600
That is how I view justice.

00:19:45.170 --> 00:19:47.800
- Where are you going?
- To find Gido-san and his wife.

00:19:47.800 --> 00:19:51.070
You'll be killed.

00:19:52.200 --> 00:19:55.200
You're no replacement for Gido

00:19:55.200 --> 00:19:59.610
if you can't see the logic behind my actions.

00:20:02.580 --> 00:20:04.630
I am Riku Hayase.

00:20:04.630 --> 00:20:07.550
I am an ordinary citizen.

00:20:07.550 --> 00:20:11.560
I cannot turn a blind eye,
knowing someone is about to die.

00:20:16.580 --> 00:20:18.290
[A]

00:20:22.810 --> 00:20:24.860
Gido-san, are you safe?

00:20:24.860 --> 00:20:28.660
I know where they're keeping Mayu.

00:20:28.660 --> 00:20:30.550
Where is she? I'll come join you.

00:20:30.550 --> 00:20:32.520
She's in the warehouse from yesterday.

00:20:32.520 --> 00:20:36.590
I'll send you the location.
This is a trap, don't come!

00:20:36.590 --> 00:20:38.340
They'll kill you!

00:20:38.340 --> 00:20:40.020
Gido-san?

00:21:01.500 --> 00:21:05.250
[I: Don't come.]
[Or you won't see your family again.]

00:22:16.210 --> 00:22:17.510
Don't move!

00:22:17.510 --> 00:22:20.510
Drop your guns!

00:22:43.320 --> 00:22:46.880
Wow, they seriously look alike!

00:22:46.880 --> 00:22:48.110
Why did you come?

00:22:48.110 --> 00:22:49.930
Where is Mayu-san?

00:23:05.620 --> 00:23:11.530
It's not every day you get to see
two of the same people.

00:23:11.530 --> 00:23:13.630
What a spectacle.

00:23:15.980 --> 00:23:21.960
Question. When making Italian meringue,
what temperature is your sugar syrup?

00:23:27.200 --> 00:23:28.540
118 degrees Celsius.

00:23:28.540 --> 00:23:31.250
Correct! Guess this one is Hayase.

00:23:36.540 --> 00:23:39.610
You leaked intel to the police.

00:23:39.610 --> 00:23:43.600
I'm sure even you can guess
the consequences of your actions.

00:23:43.600 --> 00:23:46.050
Mayu-san is innocent.

00:23:46.050 --> 00:23:48.590
Please, let her go.

00:23:48.590 --> 00:23:52.940
You really are a good cookie, aren't you?

00:23:55.190 --> 00:23:56.660
Open it.

00:24:03.630 --> 00:24:05.530
Mayu.

00:24:05.530 --> 00:24:07.470
- Mayu, are you okay?
- Mayu-san!

00:24:07.470 --> 00:24:09.870
She's been put to sleep.

00:24:10.930 --> 00:24:14.810
Now then, let's get down to business.

00:24:14.810 --> 00:24:16.370
Hey.

00:24:17.620 --> 00:24:20.610
Where is the ten billion yen?

00:24:20.610 --> 00:24:22.330
I don't know.

00:24:22.330 --> 00:24:24.320
No, don't!

00:24:27.040 --> 00:24:28.970
Where is the ten billion yen?

00:24:28.970 --> 00:24:30.550
I don't...

00:24:30.550 --> 00:24:33.570
I don't know, I swear.

00:24:33.570 --> 00:24:36.200
Ichika's the one who stole everything.

00:24:36.200 --> 00:24:39.310
Fuyuhashi!

00:24:39.310 --> 00:24:41.750
Ichika tricked me!

00:24:41.750 --> 00:24:44.290
Everything I stole was junk!

00:24:44.290 --> 00:24:47.560
Stop! Fuyuhashi, don't shoot!

00:24:47.560 --> 00:24:49.710
- Don't!
- I also saw it!

00:24:49.710 --> 00:24:51.380
Gido-san isn't lying!

00:24:51.380 --> 00:24:54.330
Ichika-san's tricking you all!

00:24:57.180 --> 00:25:00.610
Hayase-san is being led astray by Gido.

00:25:04.610 --> 00:25:07.570
I don't know what Gido told you,

00:25:07.570 --> 00:25:10.990
but who are you going to trust? Me or him?

00:25:20.280 --> 00:25:22.880
This is your last chance.

00:25:22.880 --> 00:25:25.250
Where is the ten billion yen?

00:25:25.250 --> 00:25:28.860
I don't know.

00:25:28.860 --> 00:25:30.680
Please, Goroku-san.

00:25:30.680 --> 00:25:33.400
Please let Mayu go.

00:26:05.290 --> 00:26:08.940
Mayu only joined us for the video call.

00:26:08.940 --> 00:26:11.970
She's enjoying a nice nap
at her place right now.

00:26:11.970 --> 00:26:16.420
She'll likely have no memory of the whole ordeal.

00:26:16.420 --> 00:26:20.190
I would never bring a civilian
into our affairs. You know this.

00:26:21.730 --> 00:26:23.660
Still, this is quite the conundrum.

00:26:23.660 --> 00:26:27.710
Gido-san blames Ichika-san,
and Ichika-san blames Gido-san.

00:26:27.710 --> 00:26:31.730
But I have to offer Mr. Ma

00:26:31.730 --> 00:26:35.520
the culprit's head on a platter.

00:26:35.520 --> 00:26:39.840
In other words, I get rid of one or the other.

00:26:39.840 --> 00:26:43.030
Fuyuhashi.

00:26:43.030 --> 00:26:45.100
Who would you sacrifice?

00:26:46.950 --> 00:26:50.740
We have evidence of Gido's theft.

00:26:50.740 --> 00:26:53.730
It'd be easy to make him the culprit.

00:26:53.730 --> 00:26:55.800
I'd kill Gido.

00:26:55.800 --> 00:26:57.670
Quick thinking.

00:26:57.670 --> 00:26:59.700
But you're wrong.

00:26:59.700 --> 00:27:03.020
You forgot to factor in one crucial piece.

00:27:03.020 --> 00:27:07.430
I'd get rid of Riku Hayase.

00:27:08.670 --> 00:27:14.010
We'll tell Mr. Ma the culprit was Gido
and send over a video of his death.

00:27:14.010 --> 00:27:16.210
These two are practically doppelgängers.

00:27:16.210 --> 00:27:18.710
He won't know which "Gido" dies.

00:27:18.710 --> 00:27:22.180
So we keep the more capable Gido

00:27:22.180 --> 00:27:24.510
and get rid of the useless Hayase.

00:27:24.510 --> 00:27:26.450
Wait.

00:27:27.670 --> 00:27:28.900
Get filming.

00:27:28.900 --> 00:27:30.400
Yes, Sir.

00:27:33.810 --> 00:27:35.900
Let me negotiate with Gido.

00:27:37.080 --> 00:27:40.740
I'll get him to tell me the money's location.

00:27:42.990 --> 00:27:46.410
You'd rather find the money, no?

00:27:51.720 --> 00:27:54.330
You get one minute.

00:27:57.690 --> 00:27:59.140
We'll talk, alone.

00:27:59.140 --> 00:28:00.580
Let me join you.

00:28:00.580 --> 00:28:02.750
You stay here.

00:28:05.590 --> 00:28:07.340
Close the doors.

00:28:15.180 --> 00:28:16.910
Gido.

00:28:18.950 --> 00:28:20.940
Where's the ten billion?

00:28:20.940 --> 00:28:22.750
Don't test me. I'll kill you.

00:28:22.750 --> 00:28:25.690
Can you see who this is?

00:28:27.800 --> 00:28:29.920
Bitch...

00:28:30.980 --> 00:28:32.810
Gido.

00:28:33.760 --> 00:28:36.260
I need you to do me a favor.

00:28:49.490 --> 00:28:50.860
So?

00:28:50.860 --> 00:28:53.780
Where is the ten billion yen?

00:28:56.810 --> 00:28:59.000
Fine, we'll proceed as planned.

00:28:59.870 --> 00:29:03.810
It's time we get rid of Riku Hayase.

00:29:10.420 --> 00:29:12.890
I did it.

00:29:18.990 --> 00:29:22.150
The video evidence says it all.

00:29:22.150 --> 00:29:24.940
Obviously, I'm the culprit.

00:29:25.940 --> 00:29:27.800
But none of those valuables were real.

00:29:27.800 --> 00:29:31.930
You're gullible.
I wanted to pin the blame on Ichika.

00:29:33.130 --> 00:29:34.860
Why the change of heart?

00:29:34.860 --> 00:29:38.390
Ichika convinced me to fess up.

00:29:38.390 --> 00:29:41.590
I was going to meet my end either way.

00:29:42.450 --> 00:29:46.860
I'd rather leave my crimes
at being a corrupt cop,

00:29:46.860 --> 00:29:50.980
than also get innocent people involved.

00:29:52.000 --> 00:29:56.610
Might as well take the side of justice
before I'm snuffed out, right?

00:30:03.660 --> 00:30:06.840
Where is the ten billion you stole?

00:30:06.840 --> 00:30:10.320
As soon as I speak up, it's game over for me.

00:30:10.320 --> 00:30:11.730
Fine.

00:30:11.730 --> 00:30:14.470
We'll search for it ourselves.

00:30:14.470 --> 00:30:17.600
It's a shame I can't serve you one last meal.

00:30:17.600 --> 00:30:19.490
Alas, I don't have my tools here.

00:30:19.490 --> 00:30:22.080
Goroku.

00:30:22.080 --> 00:30:25.410
Let me be the first to tell you.

00:30:27.720 --> 00:30:31.840
Your meals sure tasted great.

00:30:31.840 --> 00:30:33.740
But you know what?

00:30:34.760 --> 00:30:38.690
Your face made every meal fucking miserable.

00:30:41.820 --> 00:30:43.520
Gido-san!

00:30:50.520 --> 00:30:52.320
Gido-san!

00:31:02.390 --> 00:31:04.970
Tell Mayu...

00:31:07.870 --> 00:31:10.940
To file that divorce already.

00:31:12.660 --> 00:31:15.190
It's going to be okay.

00:31:15.190 --> 00:31:18.000
I promise, I'll protect her.

00:31:23.160 --> 00:31:25.280
Gido-san!

00:31:48.020 --> 00:31:51.100
You live to see another day.

00:31:51.100 --> 00:31:54.390
From this day forth,

00:31:54.390 --> 00:31:58.120
you will work for my organization as "Gido."

00:31:58.120 --> 00:32:02.310
You'll report back to me
with police intel, you hear?

00:32:04.650 --> 00:32:06.290
Now then, "Gido."

00:32:06.290 --> 00:32:10.560
Here's your first job.

00:32:10.560 --> 00:32:13.500
Go and bury this man.

00:32:33.630 --> 00:32:38.270
You should have known this could happen.

00:32:40.370 --> 00:32:42.670
You brought this upon yourself.

00:33:33.310 --> 00:33:36.350
Then why are you still wearing that necklace?

00:33:36.350 --> 00:33:38.350
I gave that to you.

00:33:38.350 --> 00:33:41.450
Listen, if I die...

00:33:41.450 --> 00:33:45.100
tell her I ran off with another woman.

00:33:45.980 --> 00:33:48.130
I'm counting on you.

00:35:00.420 --> 00:35:02.770
How...

00:35:02.770 --> 00:35:05.960
How did you get him to fess up?

00:35:08.200 --> 00:35:10.020
Did you threaten

00:35:10.840 --> 00:35:14.160
to kill Mayu-san?

00:35:18.040 --> 00:35:20.820
Why did you save me?

00:35:23.180 --> 00:35:26.400
Because I promised to protect you.

00:35:27.900 --> 00:35:30.170
Liar.

00:35:30.170 --> 00:35:33.740
Everything you say is a lie!

00:35:35.440 --> 00:35:39.350
The money stolen three years ago
was all you, wasn't it?

00:35:50.870 --> 00:35:54.520
I guess there's no point
in playing pretend anymore.

00:35:57.390 --> 00:36:03.830
I met Natsumi-san when I worked
at a club owned by Goroku.

00:36:03.830 --> 00:36:09.660
I told her I needed money
to save my younger sister.

00:36:09.660 --> 00:36:12.780
I had her steal that billion yen for me.

00:36:17.720 --> 00:36:21.340
Did you murder Natsumi?

00:36:21.340 --> 00:36:23.760
I wanted access to the organization's safe.

00:36:26.090 --> 00:36:29.390
I wanted Natsumi-san's status within the organization.

00:36:30.740 --> 00:36:33.530
You made me ten billion yen.

00:36:34.680 --> 00:36:36.430
Thanks.

00:36:37.240 --> 00:36:41.130
Lay a finger on me,
and your store goes up in flames.

00:36:41.130 --> 00:36:43.390
I'll make your family vanish, too.

00:36:45.870 --> 00:36:48.570
I don't understand.

00:36:48.570 --> 00:36:49.890
What do you want?

00:36:49.890 --> 00:36:52.740
Weren't you trying to save your sister?

00:36:52.740 --> 00:36:55.370
That was my goal at first.

00:36:55.370 --> 00:37:00.180
But now that I know of underworld money,
I've set my sights higher.

00:37:02.100 --> 00:37:05.340
I am going to usurp Goroku's organization.

00:37:06.860 --> 00:37:09.630
That's why I left you around.

00:37:09.630 --> 00:37:15.520
You'll build rapport in the organization
and help me crush Goroku.

00:37:17.280 --> 00:37:20.740
Once the organization is under my control,

00:37:20.740 --> 00:37:23.820
I will guarantee your family's safety.

00:37:27.180 --> 00:37:29.660
I expect great things from you,

00:37:29.660 --> 00:37:31.540
"Gido."

00:37:33.410 --> 00:37:34.940
♫ My heart just becomes empty ♫

00:37:34.940 --> 00:37:40.180
♫ My heart just becomes empty ♫

00:37:41.620 --> 00:37:47.570
♫
"Are you laughing more than usual?" ♫

00:37:47.570 --> 00:37:51.780
♫ Did such a day even exist? ♫

00:37:51.780 --> 00:37:54.040
Gido-san.

00:37:54.040 --> 00:37:56.020
Come try our new pudding.

00:37:56.020 --> 00:37:58.890
It tastes just like Dad's.

00:37:58.890 --> 00:38:00.290
I will.

00:38:00.290 --> 00:38:03.680
- See you around, kid. Careful out there.
- Yes.

00:38:20.990 --> 00:38:23.150
Gido-san!

00:38:23.150 --> 00:38:24.620
Good morning.

00:38:24.620 --> 00:38:26.490
Goodness, you're hurt.

00:38:26.490 --> 00:38:30.310
It's a part of the job.

00:38:30.310 --> 00:38:31.810
Thank you again for sending Mayu-san.

00:38:31.810 --> 00:38:35.200
She helped us perfect our newest creation!

00:38:35.200 --> 00:38:37.210
It's called the Hayase Pudding.

00:38:37.210 --> 00:38:38.980
Want to try one?

00:38:42.410 --> 00:38:44.650
Could I talk to you?

00:38:44.650 --> 00:38:49.840
I was walking home yesterday,
when someone gagged me from behind.

00:38:49.840 --> 00:38:52.420
By the time I came to, I was back home.

00:38:52.420 --> 00:38:55.550
I was wearing a different outfit as well.

00:38:56.590 --> 00:38:59.040
You must have been terrified.

00:39:01.380 --> 00:39:04.600
Don't worry, nothing has happened to you.

00:39:04.600 --> 00:39:08.010
I promise no more danger will befall you.

00:39:10.440 --> 00:39:13.180
Has something happened to Gido?

00:39:14.960 --> 00:39:16.900
Your husband...

00:39:18.400 --> 00:39:21.400
He embezzled money from a certain organization.

00:39:21.400 --> 00:39:23.650
His life was in danger here.

00:39:23.650 --> 00:39:26.590
He fled to a Southeast Asian country.

00:39:27.510 --> 00:39:30.650
Then Gido is safe?

00:39:31.940 --> 00:39:33.410
Yes.

00:39:34.540 --> 00:39:36.080
However,

00:39:36.080 --> 00:39:38.940
he left with another woman.

00:39:41.290 --> 00:39:43.540
I was told to give you this.

00:39:47.500 --> 00:39:50.670
[Divorce Forms]

00:39:55.860 --> 00:40:01.040
He wanted to end things with you for good.

00:40:17.600 --> 00:40:21.820
Hayase-san, what are you planning to do now?

00:40:23.730 --> 00:40:28.020
I will arrest my wife's murderer
and return home to my family.

00:40:28.020 --> 00:40:29.780
I made a promise to them.

00:40:34.080 --> 00:40:38.660
Would you like to try a Hayase Pudding?

00:40:40.450 --> 00:40:44.090
Gido never liked sweet things.

00:40:44.090 --> 00:40:48.620
I think I can forget him,
if I see you eating one.

00:41:13.570 --> 00:41:15.540
Thank you.

00:42:04.850 --> 00:42:10.190
I won't tell anyone your true identity.

00:42:10.940 --> 00:42:14.800
I'll leave your store as well.

00:42:18.940 --> 00:42:23.810
But please tell me your story
once everything is over.

00:42:26.970 --> 00:42:28.900
I pray

00:42:28.900 --> 00:42:33.600
that you'll be reunited with your family soon.

00:42:50.020 --> 00:42:52.100
That necklace.

00:42:54.380 --> 00:42:57.090
I made sure to return it to Gido-san.

00:43:03.520 --> 00:43:09.690
Gido-san treasured you.

00:43:13.930 --> 00:43:16.170
He cared for you.

00:43:18.270 --> 00:43:21.270
With all his heart.

00:43:30.660 --> 00:43:32.520
Thank you.

00:43:48.160 --> 00:43:50.830
[Again | Mr. Children
(Toys Factory)]

00:43:55.210 --> 00:43:57.650
You could at least knock.

00:43:57.650 --> 00:44:00.160
Gido is dead.

00:44:03.980 --> 00:44:08.720
And here I thought he'd kill the fake.

00:44:08.720 --> 00:44:10.480
Oh, well.

00:44:10.480 --> 00:44:12.960
I suppose you'll have to do.

00:44:12.960 --> 00:44:17.140
Bring me evidence that ties Goroku
and our whale together.

00:44:17.140 --> 00:44:20.470
Crush the whale and Goroku's organization,

00:44:20.470 --> 00:44:22.660
and I will guarantee your family's safety.

00:44:22.660 --> 00:44:27.360
A woman named Ichika Kogo
wants to usurp Goroku's organization.

00:44:32.300 --> 00:44:35.110
Now that's an interesting lead.

00:44:35.110 --> 00:44:37.240
Sounds promising.

00:44:37.240 --> 00:44:39.210
Tell me more.

00:44:39.210 --> 00:44:42.990
Ichika's the one who murdered my wife.

00:44:42.990 --> 00:44:47.870
Promise me you'll arrest her,
and have her fess up her crimes.

00:44:47.870 --> 00:44:57.790
Timing and subtitles by
"🍰 The Pastry Detectives 🔍" Team @Viki.com

00:44:57.790 --> 00:45:00.140
You're looking sharper.

00:45:01.830 --> 00:45:05.650
You'd do a fine job replacing Gido.

00:45:05.650 --> 00:45:07.920
I'm not a replacement.

00:45:10.760 --> 00:45:13.610
I am Ayumi Gido.

00:45:18.140 --> 00:45:21.060
We're bringing Ichika Kogo down.

00:45:26.400 --> 00:45:30.230
This is where my reboot really begins.

00:45:32.750 --> 00:45:36.990
[Reboot]

00:45:36.990 --> 00:45:38.670
How about crushing Goroku with me?
[Next, Episode 7: Awakening]

00:45:38.670 --> 00:45:42.550
You're acting like Gido. Why?
[The birth of a new Gido]

00:45:42.550 --> 00:45:43.860
I can't back down now.
[Giving up to evil in the name of justice]

00:45:43.860 --> 00:45:46.210
I'm sure you wish you could kill me now.

00:45:46.210 --> 00:45:48.330
Do you recognize this individual?
[A burning sense of helplessness and frustration..]

00:45:48.330 --> 00:45:49.570
Quit acting so soft.
[Fuyuhashi makes a decision for the sake of his 'family']

00:45:49.570 --> 00:45:51.010
It's sorta frustrating,
[It's almost time for the reboot to be discovered]

00:45:51.010 --> 00:45:53.270
always following Goroku-san's orders.
[A tense moment that will decide their fate]

00:45:53.270 --> 00:45:54.840
You're the one pushing yourself.

00:45:54.840 --> 00:45:58.300
You take on all the dirty work yourself.
[This drama is a work of fiction.]